<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="de">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Kontaktformular Demo</title>
<style>
*{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0}
body{background:#0a0a0a;color:#f5f2ec;font-family:Arial,sans-serif}
header{padding:20px;background:#111;border-bottom:1px solid #2a2a2a}
a{color:#e8572a;text-decoration:none}
.wrap{max-width:800px;margin:auto;padding:45px 20px}
.card{background:#131310;border:1px solid #2a2a2a;border-radius:18px;padding:28px}
h1{font-size:clamp(2.3rem,6vw,4rem);margin-bottom:15px}
p{color:#b8b1a7;line-height:1.7;margin-bottom:25px}
input,textarea,select,button{width:100%;padding:14px;margin-top:12px;border-radius:8px;border:1px solid #333;background:#0f0f0f;color:white}
textarea{min-height:130px}
button{background:#e8572a;border:none;font-weight:bold;cursor:pointer}
.success{display:none;color:#28c840;margin-top:15px}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<header>
<a href="modelle.html">← Zurück zu Modelle</a>
</header>

<div class="wrap">
<div class="card">
<h1>Kontaktformular Demo</h1>
<p>Ein einfaches Formular für Kontaktanfragen, Rückrufe oder Angebotswünsche. In dieser Demo wird nichts verschickt.</p>

<form onsubmit="submitForm(event)">
<input required placeholder="Name">
<input required type="email" placeholder="E-Mail">
<select>
<option>Allgemeine Anfrage</option>
<option>Rückruf gewünscht</option>
<option>Angebot gewünscht</option>
<option>Terminwunsch</option>
</select>
<textarea placeholder="Nachricht"></textarea>
<button type="submit">Nachricht senden</button>
<div id="success" class="success">Demo-Nachricht wurde erfasst.</div>
</form>
</div>
</div>

<script>
function submitForm(e){
e.preventDefault();
document.getElementById("success").style.display="block";
e.target.reset();
}
</script>

</body>
</html>
